      fillText: 'Algorithmic systems used in high-stakes domains raise questions of _______ when their decisions cannot be explained. The EU AI Act requires _______ oversight for high-risk systems, though critics argue this creates _______ for innovation. The risk of _______ bias is amplified when training data reflects historical inequalities. Ultimately, AI _______ requires engagement from technologists, lawyers, and affected communities alike.',
